===2020年香港立法會選舉===
於2020年香港立法會選舉，[[黃碧雲|黃碧雲]]角逐連任。黃首先在[[2020年香港立法會選舉民主黨黨內甄選|黨內初選]]面對[[袁海文|袁海文]]挑戰，雖然成功出線，但在5月17日的民主黨特別會員大會中取得50張反對票，佔所有票數近1／4，是眾多民主黨候選人之冠。<ref name="Hk01-20200517">{{cite web |author1=周禮希 |author2=吳倬安 |author3=鄧家琪 |title=民主黨特別會員大會通過7人籌組參選隊伍　強調尊重泛民協調爭35+ |url=https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/474165/%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E7%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%8C%E7%B5%84%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E9%9A%8A%E4%BC%8D-%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E5%8D%94%E8%AA%BF%E7%88%AD35 |accessdate=2020-07-14 |archive-date=2020-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714154318/https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/474165/%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E7%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%8C%E7%B5%84%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E9%9A%8A%E4%BC%8D-%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E5%8D%94%E8%AA%BF%E7%88%AD35 |dead-url=no }}</ref>及後黃碧雲代表民主黨出選九龍西地區直選民主派初選，但於所有候選人當中排名第7，最終黃碧雲承認初選落敗，宣布不會參與9月大選。<ref name="TheStandNews-20200714">{{cite web |title=黃碧雲承認初選落敗　不報名參選立法會 |url=https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%BB%83%E7%A2%A7%E9%9B%B2%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8%E8%90%BD%E6%95%97-%E4%B8%8D%E5%A0%B1%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83/ |accessdate=2020-07-14 |archive-date=2020-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714201206/https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%BB%83%E7%A2%A7%E9%9B%B2%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8%E8%90%BD%E6%95%97-%E4%B8%8D%E5%A0%B1%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

